 at the wrong moment. I was having my bath, and Elsie told him I wasn’t in. Here: give him these three marks when you see him—what I can do I do gladly—and tell him I can’t afford any more, so he’d better apply to somebody else—to Vladimir Isakovich Davidov, perhaps.”

